In addition , notwithstanding any other provision of this Privacy Policy , in the event that Football Talk LLC merges with , or substantially all of its assets are acquired by , another business entity , personal information that users have provided at any point in time to Football Talk LLC may be released or transferred to the new business entity as one of the transferred assets .
