This is cookie that remembers your choice of the mobile or desktop site .
The cookie lasts beyond your current session , but no personal or sensitive information is collected .
Ident ( IDENT , SkipIdent ) :
These cookies are used by the homepage to remember whether y you have elected to always skip the site 's intro sequence .
